# Lesson-by-Lesson Research Evidence

---

## 1. `scrambled_story` — Fluency and Connected Speech

**Why it works:** Reassembling a story and then reading it aloud forces the student to process sentence structure and then produce it orally. Repeated oral reading of connected text is the most evidence-backed method for building spoken fluency.

