## 2. `pace_difference` — Speaking Rate Control

**Why it works:** Deliberately varying speaking speed builds conscious control over tempo — one of the six core voice signals Bantrly measures. Research on prosody training shows that visual feedback (like Bantrly's waveform) paired with rate control exercises produces measurable improvement.

