## 3. `emotion_difference` — Prosody and Expression

**Why it works:** Emotional prosody — the way voice changes to convey feeling — is a trainable skill. Research shows it develops throughout childhood and is directly linked to social communication ability. Training students to hear and reproduce emotional prosody improves both their speaking expressiveness and their social intelligence.

