## 4. `character_read` — Vocal Variety and Delivery

**Why it works:** Role-based speaking — reading in a character's voice — is a well-established drama-in-education technique. It removes self-consciousness and produces higher expressive range than unstructured speaking tasks. The character badge acts as a cognitive anchor that shapes delivery without requiring the student to consciously decide how to sound.

