## 5. `tongue_twister` — Pronunciation and Articulation

**Why it works:** Tongue twisters are one of the oldest evidence-based tools for training specific phoneme production. The graduated speed structure (slow → medium → fast) is directly supported by research on pronunciation acquisition — accuracy must be established before speed is introduced.

