## 6. `speed_reader` — Fluency Under Time Pressure

**Why it works:** Timed oral reading builds automaticity — the ability to read words without conscious effort, which frees cognitive resources for expression and comprehension. Research shows oral reading practice in high school correlates more closely with achievement gains than silent reading.

