## 7. `listen_and_echo` — Listening into Speaking

**Why it works:** Elicited imitation — hearing something and immediately reproducing it — is one of the most studied speaking training methods in second language acquisition research. It trains the auditory-motor loop and is the core mechanism behind how children first learn to speak.

