## 8. `scene_speak` — Descriptive Speaking and Task Adherence

**Why it works:** Describing a scene requires the student to organize and produce language spontaneously — the closest Bantrly gets to open-ended speaking. The paragraph read-aloud that precedes it gives the student language scaffolding before they produce their own description, which directly reduces cognitive load and anxiety.

