## 10. `refresher` — Retention of Speaking Skills

**Why it works:** The refresher lesson is a direct implementation of spaced retrieval practice — one of the most consistently replicated findings in cognitive science. Bringing back previously learned skills after a delay strengthens memory traces and prevents forgetting.

