## 11. `topic_read` — Reading Fluency on Self-Chosen Content

**Why it works:** Student choice of topic increases motivation and engagement, which increases the amount of time students spend practising — and it is reading volume (time on task) that most strongly predicts fluency gains. The passage itself is already written; the student's only job is to read it aloud well.

