## 12. `delivery_flashcard` — Stress, Tone, and Volume Control

**Why it works:** Word stress and sentence-level prosody are trainable through explicit instruction and immediate feedback. Research on visual pitch contour training (showing students their waveform alongside a model) shows significant measurable improvement. The flashcard format delivers the instruction quickly and the perform step captures the result.

